{"tid":845543,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉斯維加斯警方重啟「C.朗強姦案」調查！","createTime":"2018-10-02T17:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:14:25.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"285ba002f2fc9284a29b41a285c4d332f0d1babf","tid":845543,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"拉斯維加斯警方日前宣佈，對一起發生在2009年6月的強姦案重新啟動調查，雖然公告中沒有說明更多信息，但據媒體報導，這起案件的嫌疑人正是C.朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n　　34歲的凱瑟琳-馬祖爾加對德國《明鏡週刊》曝料，稱2009年在拉斯維加斯酒店內遭到葡萄牙球星強暴，如今尋求案件重審。<br />\n<br />\n　　在拉斯維加斯警方的這份聲明中寫道：「我們正在跟蹤受害者提供的信息，這是一個正在進行中的調查，目前不會有更多信息透露。」聲明中寫出了事件的具體事件：2009年6月13日。據《每日郵報》等媒體報導，C.朗拿度正是這起案件的嫌疑人。"},{"pid":"a93d96f18a9e7d6332c00d3d16f7fce6b6c12c7e","tid":845543,"uid":65298,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"對C朗好失望<br />\n<br />\n仲以為佢係gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6216ccdf87c385f19c90394eff8c955108fdb705","tid":845543,"uid":166434,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"屈撚完未<br />\n一轉會就全世界都搞鳩人地"},{"pid":"5c9e1db67ae1d43530da5e6c3c491faf7612716d","tid":845543,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"簽左和解協議書收埋錢<br />\n仲可以翻告架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd08edd549bc4cecb0c596e4b92c6db93222ec35","tid":845543,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6f971e6ebc2bf2dfae4493c483405e3fc2b0fdf","tid":845543,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd08edd549bc4cecb0c596e4b92c6db93222ec35","tid":845543,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c9e1db67ae1d43530da5e6c3c491faf7612716d","tid":845543,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"簽左和解協議書收埋錢<br />\n仲可以翻告架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi